<div id="post-1688" class="post-1688 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-abc-news category-blog-nate-thayer category-cambodia category-free-speach category-freelance-journalism category-freelance-journalist category-freelance-photography category-freelancers-rights category-journalistic-ethics category-media-ethics category-nate-thayer category-nate-thayer-blog category-pay-the-writer category-plagiarism category-sympathy-for-the-devil-by-nate-thayer category-ted-koppel category-war-correspondent tag-abc-news tag-cambodia tag-freelance-journalism tag-journalism-ethics tag-khmer-rouge tag-nate-thayer tag-nate-thayer-blog tag-sympathy-for-the-devil tag-ted-koppel">

	
	<h2 class="title"><a href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/" rel="bookmark" title="How Ted Koppel and ABC TV Tried to Steal my Life&nbsp;Work">How Ted Koppel and ABC TV Tried to Steal my Life&nbsp;Work</a></h2>
	<a class="date" href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/">
		<span class="day">8</span>
		<span class="month">Dec</span>
	</a>

	

	<div class="entry">
		<p><strong>How Ted Koppel and ABC TV Tried to Steal my Life Work</strong></p>
<p><em><strong>By Nate Thayer</strong></em></p>
<p>December 8, 2013</p>
<p>I am banned by legal agreement to write the following: ABC Television/ Disney Corporation, after seven years in court, where they attempted to bankrupt me and ruin my reputation for objecting to them stealing fifteen years of my life work, buckled and paid me. They have the legal right to take back the money they finally paid me&#8211;which actually all went to lawyers and taxes&#8211;if I open my mouth.</p>
<p>Fuck them.</p>
<p>Good luck getting blood from a stone while trying to attempt to muzzle a free person in a free society while claiming you are an icon of the free press and free speech</p>
<p>So here goes&#8230;..</p>
<p><span class="userContent">On July 25, 1997, I was the first outsider to meet Pol Pot since he killed 1.8 million people 20 years before. </span></p>
<p><span class="userContent">It was, for a couple of days, the biggest story in the world. I, as a freelance journalist, had the only photographs and vide<span class="text_exposed_show">o and eyewitness account that existed since Pol Pot did what he did. It was a tumultuous few days of dealing with the very worst of what the big media companies represented. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">Ted Koppel, of ABC Nightline, flew to Bangkok to view the video and signed a written contract for &#8220;North American video rights only for 7 days.&#8221; ABC America&#8211;owned by Disney&#8211;told Koppel to sign whatever Thayer asks for&#8211;our lawyers will deal with it later. He is just a freelancer. Give him whatever he wants. We can bankrupt him if he objects. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">As soon as ABC, which had exactly zero correspondents in Southeast Asia, got a hold of a copy of the tape, which Ted Koppel personally and in writing promised he would not allow any frame grabs to be made into still pictures, or allow the video to be distributed to anyone outside of Nightline, or allow the transcript of the text of the video to be shown to anyone else, ABC created the below frame grabs from the video, distributed it personally to numerous news outfits, including the AP and the New York Times, where it appeared on their front page above the fold, and ABC placed them on their website crediting themselves with having taken the image.</span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">My picture, credited to ABC TV, was published on the front pages of hundreds of newspapers around the world, my footage was distributed around the globe, and my story was written in virtually every major news organ on earth, credited to ABC TV, before I actually had written my own story . which was published with the integrity and dignity and seriousness it deserved in my excellent publication, the Far Eastern Economic Review.<br />
</span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1689" alt="1018923 Pol Pot ABC Frame Grab Pic" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg?w=490" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg 411w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg?w=150 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 411px) 100vw, 411px"   /></a></span></span></p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_1691" style="width: 310px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/abcstolen-july-29-1997-1108-am-edt.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1691" data-attachment-id="1691" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/abcstolen-july-29-1997-1108-am-edt/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/abcstolen-july-29-1997-1108-am-edt.jpg" data-orig-size="300,233" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="abcstolen july 29 1997 1108 am edt" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/abcstolen-july-29-1997-1108-am-edt.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/abcstolen-july-29-1997-1108-am-edt.jpg?w=300" class="size-full wp-image-1691 " alt="ABC TV stolen pictures frame grab from my copyrighted work. Count them--four separate credits demanding ABC be given credit for photographs taken when ABC did b not even have a staff person in all of Southeast Asia. This photo was hand delivered to the New York Times, The AP and posted on ABC's website" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/abcstolen-july-29-1997-1108-am-edt.jpg?w=490" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/abcstolen-july-29-1997-1108-am-edt.jpg 300w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/abcstolen-july-29-1997-1108-am-edt.jpg?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px"   /></a><p id="caption-attachment-1691" class="wp-caption-text">ABC TV stolen pictures frame grab from my copyrighted work. Count them&#8211;four separate credits demanding ABC be given credit for photographs taken when ABC did b not even have a staff person in all of Southeast Asia. This photo was hand delivered to the New York Times, The AP and posted on ABC&#8217;s website</p></div>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">ABC distributed transcripts of the trial of Pol Pot I had made and allowed other news organizations to view the video tape with strict instructions to credit ABC for the images and story, and then refused to pay me anything unless I signed a release that they did nothing wrong and I promised not to take legal action against them. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">I refused. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">Nine months later, I won the Peabody award as a &#8220;correspondent for ABC Nightline.&#8221; </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">Ted Koppel called me up, nervous, to congratulate me. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">I said &#8220;Fuck you! Where is my fucking money? I am going to go to the Peabody awards ceremony and refuse the award and tell the planet what unethical thieves ABC are and how you, Ted Koppel, acted as their pimp.&#8221; I was then banned from attending the award ceremony, escorted out of the Waldorf Astoria hotel banquet room by security guards. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">I spent seven years in court fighting ABC. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">I won, sort of. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">It sucked the life out of me, which was the exact intention of ABC: to make my life as miserable and expensive and distracted as possible to punish me for objecting to bald plagiarism, fraud, and theft. They tried to bankrupt me and ruin my reputation. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">But ABC fucked with the wrong person. They will never fuck with Nate Thayer again. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">It was worth it. They thought I would back down in the face of their team of hundreds of staff lawyers and corporate power. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">I refused. </span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">Such is the life of freelance journalism.</span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">Every freelance journalist alive has suffered under the corporate jackboot of the ABC&#8217;s of the media world, their work stolen and never compensated. Usually it is not possible to pay for a legal team to fight them to get remunerated for one&#8217;s work.<br />
</span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">Above and below are a couple of the still pictures, still available by a simple Google search online.</span></span></p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_1689" style="width: 421px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1689" data-attachment-id="1689" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg" data-orig-size="411,276" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="1018923 Pol Pot ABC Frame Grab Pic" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg?w=411" class="size-full wp-image-1689" alt="Another ABC frame grab of my still pictures, taken after 15 years of work, which they distributed to the planet and took credit for" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg?w=490" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg 411w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg?w=150 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/1018923-pol-pot-abc-frame-grab-pic.jpg?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 411px) 100vw, 411px"   /></a><p id="caption-attachment-1689" class="wp-caption-text">Another ABC frame grab of my still pictures, taken after 15 years of work, which they distributed to the planet and took credit for</p></div>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">These are just some examples of the still picture ABC frame grab&#8217;s ABC took from the video and distributed to the world, voiding scores of contracts I had sold for my stills for exclusive rights.I had scores of contracts for the sale of still pictures, video, and stories cancelled around the globe overnight.<br />
</span></span></p>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="text_exposed_show">ABC tried to take credit for 15 years of my life work. Below is one of my original still photographs, which became worthless overnight because  a degraded version was available for free from the ABC website.</span></span></p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_1693" style="width: 410px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot_late-trial-nate-thayer.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1693" data-attachment-id="1693" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/cambodia-pol-potwalk-3/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot_late-trial-nate-thayer.jpg" data-orig-size="400,301" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;EPA&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;+MAGS OUT+, ONE TIME USE ONLY, NO ARCHIVES, ++ SWEDEN OUT, DAILY MAIL AND SUNDAY TIMES OUT ++\nNotorious Khmer Rouge leader Pol Pot is assisted by soldiers as he arrives to attend his trial 25 July during which he was denounced by former comrades at the Khmer Rouge stronghold of Anlong Veng in northern Cambodia. The veteran revolutionary and three of his top commanders were \&quot;tried\&quot; and sentenced to life imprisonment for the murder of former Khmer Rouge defence minister Son Sen and his family. AFP PHOTO Copyright-1997 Nate THAYER\/Tom KELLER &amp; Associates +MAGS OUT+, ONE TIME USE ONLY, NO ARCHIVES ++ SWEDEN OUT - DAILY MAIL &amp; SUNDAY TIMES OUT ++&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;CAMBODIA-POL-POT\/WALK&quot;}" data-image-title="CAMBODIA-POL-POT/WALK" data-image-description="&lt;p&gt;+MAGS OUT+, ONE TIME USE ONLY, NO ARCHIVES, ++ SWEDEN OUT, DAILY MAIL AND SUNDAY TIMES OUT ++&lt;br /&gt;
Notorious Khmer Rouge leader Pol Pot is assisted by soldiers as he arrives to attend his trial 25 July during which he was denounced by former comrades at the Khmer Rouge stronghold of Anlong Veng in northern Cambodia. The veteran revolutionary and three of his top commanders were &#8220;tried&#8221; and sentenced to life imprisonment for the murder of former Khmer Rouge defence minister Son Sen and his family. AFP PHOTO Copyright-1997 Nate THAYER/Tom KELLER &amp;amp; Associates +MAGS OUT+, ONE TIME USE ONLY, NO ARCHIVES ++ SWEDEN OUT &#8211; DAILY MAIL &amp;amp; SUNDAY TIMES OUT ++&lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot_late-trial-nate-thayer.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot_late-trial-nate-thayer.jpg?w=400" class="size-full wp-image-1693" alt="CAMBODIA-POL-POT/WALK" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot_late-trial-nate-thayer.jpg?w=490" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot_late-trial-nate-thayer.jpg 400w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot_late-trial-nate-thayer.jpg?w=150 150w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot_late-trial-nate-thayer.jpg?w=300 300w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px"   /></a><p id="caption-attachment-1693" class="wp-caption-text">One of my actual still photographs&#8211;taken by me&#8211;with a Nikon F-4 on July 25, 1997&#8212;the first pictures of Pol Pot taken since he murdered 1.8 million people during his 3 years 8 months and 20 days in power</p></div>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot-abc.jpg"><img data-attachment-id="1692" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/polpot-abc/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot-abc.jpg" data-orig-size="300,233" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="polpot.abc" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot-abc.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot-abc.jpg?w=300" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1692" alt="polpot.abc" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot-abc.jpg?w=490" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot-abc.jpg 300w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpot-abc.jpg?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px"   /></a></p>
<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_1694" style="width: 283px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpottrialmine.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1694" data-attachment-id="1694" data-permalink="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/polpottrialmine/" data-orig-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpottrialmine.jpg" data-orig-size="273,184" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-image-title="polpottrialmine" data-image-description="" data-medium-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpottrialmine.jpg?w=273" data-large-file="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpottrialmine.jpg?w=273" class="size-full wp-image-1694" alt="My still photograph, which became worthless on the international market after ABC TV America stole my pictures and tried to take credit for 15 years of my life work" src="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpottrialmine.jpg?w=490" srcset="https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpottrialmine.jpg 273w, https://natethayer.files.wordpress.com/2013/12/polpottrialmine.jpg?w=150 150w" sizes="(max-width: 273px) 100vw, 273px"   /></a><p id="caption-attachment-1694" class="wp-caption-text">My still photograph, which became worthless on the international market after ABC TV America stole my pictures and tried to take credit for 15 years of my life work</p></div>
<div id="jp-post-flair" class="sharedaddy sd-like-enabled sd-sharing-enabled"><div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"><div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-icon-text sd-sharing"><h3 class="sd-title">Share this:</h3><div class="sd-content"><ul><li class="share-twitter"><a rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" data-shared="sharing-twitter-1688" class="share-twitter sd-button share-icon" href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/?share=twitter" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Twitter"><span>Twitter</span></a></li><li class="share-facebook"><a rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" data-shared="sharing-facebook-1688" class="share-facebook sd-button share-icon" href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/?share=facebook" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Facebook"><span>Facebook</span></a></li><li class="share-reddit"><a rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" data-shared="" class="share-reddit sd-button share-icon" href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/?share=reddit" target="_blank" title="Click to share on Reddit"><span>Reddit</span></a></li><li class="share-linkedin"><a rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" data-shared="sharing-linkedin-1688" class="share-linkedin sd-button share-icon" href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/?share=linkedin" target="_blank" title="Click to share on LinkedIn"><span>LinkedIn</span></a></li><li class="share-email"><a rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" data-shared="" class="share-email sd-button share-icon" href="https://natethayer.wordpress.com/2013/12/08/how-ted-koppel-and-abc-tv-tried-to-steal-my-life-work/?share=email" target="_blank" title="Click to email this to a friend"><span>Email</span></a></li><li class="share-print"><a rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer" da